name: BOYFUSION (aka YaoiGen)
description:
This model was previously named YaoiGen*

BOYFUSION has been trained on 1000's of bara, yaoi, and actual photographs of male models on top of Anything V3 with a focus on stable nude output with as little inpainting as possible. Can output SFW and Hentai as well.

If you feel like supporting further development & caffeine addiction:

  • buymeacoffee.com/atiredhamster

Current Recommended Settings

  • Steps: 26-32

  • Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras | Euler A

  • CFG: 7-10

  • Denoising: 0.6

  • HiRes Steps: 10

  • Upscaler: NMKD UltraYandere

  • Recommended VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema
